# Orca
A reconfigurable dataflow accelerator to accelerate the dynamic task flow.

# Arch



# Description

There is a top level controller to control the all system.

There are several tasks type which can be mainly classified as dynamically or statically.
These two type can be regarded as the number of job will be created by the parent tasks.

There are several tasks type which can be mainly classified as the following types.
- unicast type
- sub unicast type
- 1-D multicast type
- multicast type


- Dynamically
   - Data Dependence Task
   - If-else based Task
   - Parallelisable Task
- Statically
   - Root Task
      - The task which is the first task to be executed
   - Sharable Task







